                       References
==============================================================

- The Physics of Plasmas T.J.M. Boyd and J.J. Sanderson,
  Cambridge University Presss

- Introduction to Plasma Physicss with Space and Laboratory Applications,
  Donald A. Gurnett and Amitava Bhattacharjee, Cambridge University Presss

- Plasma Physics for Astrophysics, Russel M. Kulsrud
  Princeton University Presss

- Stellar Magnetism, Leon Mestel, Oxford Science Publication

- Magnetohydrodynamics of Laboratory and Astrophysical Plasmas
  Goedbloed, Keppens, and Poedts

- Ideal magnetohydrodynamic theory of magnetic fusion systems, J. P. Friedberg, Reviews of Modern Physics, Vol 54, No 3, July 1982
